Package: xlversion
Title: Versioning and change tracking for Excel files (.xlsx)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Vera", "Gonçalves", , "vera.maria.dg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `xlversion` provides tools to create fingerprints, snapshots, and intelligent comparisons of Excel files at the sheet level. Ideal for version control, auditing, and data pipelines.
